class Solution {
public:
    int waysToSplitArray(vector<int>& nums) {
        vector<long> cumsum;
        long s = 0;
        for (int i  : nums) {
            s += i;
            cumsum.push_back(s);
        }

        int c=0;
        long ls;
        long rs;
        for (int i=0; i<nums.size()-1; i++) {
            ls = cumsum[i];
            rs = s-ls;

            if(ls>=rs) {
                c++;
            }
        }  
        return c;
    }
}; ^x3FcaHrC
